<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 24 Oct 2023 12:12:06 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>为什么世界媒体相信哈马斯关于加沙医院爆炸的骗局？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-24/ty-article-opinion/.premium/why-did-the-world-media-believe-the-hamas-hoax-about-the-gaza-hospital-explosion/0000018b-5c6d-d00f-a9bf-7c7dd2d40000</link><description>哈马斯管理的加沙卫生部就像奥威尔式的“真理部”一样可靠。但这并没有阻止世界各地的记者争先恐后地放大恐怖组织的说法，即阿赫利医院的爆炸是以色列的空袭</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Oct 2023 11:45:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-24/ty-article-opinion/.premium/why-did-the-world-media-believe-the-hamas-hoax-about-the-gaza-hospital-explosion/0000018b-5c6d-d00f-a9bf-7c7dd2d40000</guid></item><item><title>由于限制越来越多，以色列军队将巴勒斯坦活动人士驱逐出希伯伦的家</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-24/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-expels-palestinian-activist-from-hebron-home-amid-increasing-restrictions/0000018b-6129-d307-adbb-6539a3aa0000</link><description>以色列国防军士兵要求伊萨·阿姆罗在战争期间离开他位于该市以色列控制区的家。居住在希伯伦该地区的其他巴勒斯坦人表示，由于以色列国防军试图控制该市的行动，实际上“完全禁止外出”</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Oct 2023 11:30:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-24/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-expels-palestinian-activist-from-hebron-home-amid-increasing-restrictions/0000018b-6129-d307-adbb-6539a3aa0000</guid></item><item><title>现已获释的以色列祖母讲述了哈马斯被囚禁的经历，称“政府抛弃了我们”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-24/ty-article/.premium/85-year-old-israeli-grandmother-recounts-hamas-captivity-says-government-deserted-us/0000018b-615d-d312-a1fb-f77f9aea0000</link><description>85 岁的 Yocheved Lifshitz 是周一晚些时候获释的两名妇女之一，大约 220 名人质仍留在哈马斯手中。在特拉维夫一家医院，她揭露了哈马斯的加沙地道、医疗情况，并讲述了10月7日的暴力绑架事件</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Oct 2023 11:18:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-24/ty-article/.premium/85-year-old-israeli-grandmother-recounts-hamas-captivity-says-government-deserted-us/0000018b-615d-d312-a1fb-f77f9aea0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警方逮捕一名涉嫌支持哈马斯袭击的女演员</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-24/ty-article/.premium/israeli-police-arrest-actress-over-online-post-allegedly-endorsing-hamas-attack/0000018b-612c-d307-adbb-653c3fd00000</link><description>梅萨·阿卜杜勒·哈迪 (Maisa Abd Elhadi) 被捕之前，国家检察官正式支持审判任何赞扬哈马斯在以色列南部犯下暴行的人</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Oct 2023 10:52:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-24/ty-article/.premium/israeli-police-arrest-actress-over-online-post-allegedly-endorsing-hamas-attack/0000018b-612c-d307-adbb-653c3fd00000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡的部长们希望“把他的头放在盘子上”，但拒绝公开这么说</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-24/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-ministers-desire-to-put-his-head-on-a-platter-refuse-to-say-so-openly/0000018b-60f1-d2b2-addf-66f9e33a0000</link><description>经过 17 天的战争后，利库德集团部长们加大了对内塔尼亚胡的攻击力度，但并不准备辞职。具有讽刺意味的是，由甘茨和艾森科特组成的战时内阁从利库德集团那里获得的支持比原来的内阁要多得多</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Oct 2023 10:44:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-24/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-ministers-desire-to-put-his-head-on-a-platter-refuse-to-say-so-openly/0000018b-60f1-d2b2-addf-66f9e33a0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡告诉马克龙，“哈马斯是新的纳粹”；被释放的以色列人质讲述被囚禁的经历</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-24/ty-article-live/two-elderly-israeli-hostages-freed-from-gaza-frances-macron-to-visit-israel-ramallah/0000018b-5f5d-d2b2-addf-7f7dcd790000</link><description>法国总统马克龙抵达以色列，会见内塔尼亚胡、赫尔佐格、人质家属和巴勒斯坦权力机构主席阿巴斯 ■ 两名从哈马斯囚禁中获释的老年妇女 ■ 内塔尼亚胡和拜登发表讲话，白宫表示“现在不是停火的时候” ■ 至少 1,300 人死亡自 10 月 7 日起由哈马斯控制 ■ 哈马斯管理的卫生部：5,300 名巴勒斯坦人被杀，18,000 人受伤</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Oct 2023 09:27:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isP