le/.premium/israel-plays-a-nerve-wracking-waiting-game-ahead-of-a-gaza-ground-offensive/0000018b-5e32-d8e2-a1eb-ff36c1350000</link><description>加沙地面行动的拖延加剧了政府与军队之间以及政府内部的信任危机 ■ 在释放两名以色列老年妇女后，哈马斯希望部分释放人质能够减轻其面临的国际压力在下面</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Oct 2023 03:00:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-24/ty-article/.premium/israel-plays-a-nerve-wracking-waiting-game-ahead-of-a-gaza-ground-offensive/0000018b-5e32-d8e2-a1eb-ff36c1350000</guid></item><item><title>“安德森·库珀说：我有一段你被绑架儿子的视频”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2023-10-24/ty-article-podcast/anderson-cooper-said-i-have-a-video-of-your-kidnapped-son/0000018b-5e1a-d8e2-a1eb-ff1e67b50000</link><description></description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Oct 2023 22:14:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2023-10-24/ty-article-podcast/anderson-cooper-said-i-have-a-video-of-your-kidnapped-son/0000018b-5e1a-d8e2-a1eb-ff1e67b50000</guid></item><item><title>以色列的首要任务必须是释放人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-10-24/ty-article-opinion/israels-top-priority-must-be-to-free-the-hostages/0000018b-5e35-d473-a5fb-7efd82530000</link><description></description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Oct 2023 21:32:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-10-24/ty-article-opinion/israels-top-priority-must-be-to-free-the-hostages/0000018b-5e35-d473-a5fb-7efd82530000</guid></item><item><title>不要让对哈马斯报仇的呼声压制我们的良心</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-24/ty-article-opinion/.premium/dont-let-calls-for-revenge-against-hamas-silence-our-conscience/0000018b-5d90-d8e2-a1eb-ff966bca0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Oct 2023 21:19:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-24/ty-article-opinion/.premium/dont-let-calls-for-revenge-against-hamas-silence-our-conscience/0000018b-5d90-d8e2-a1eb-ff966bca0000</guid></item><item>